  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After the Great Clash, the world was destroyed, broken and divided into several realms. Each realm was managed by Gods, but the Gods abandoned humans.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a 'Contender', you have a mission to advance to the throne of God. When a Contender reaches the throne of a God, they are crowned as a new God.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various traps and footholds await you on your way to the throne of God. Break through these safely and advance towards the top.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you throw a sphere with your right hand, after a while it will move to where it was. This is the Contender's unique power 'Blink'.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Destroy medals hidden throughout the realm to level up. Leveling up has several benefits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your challenge progress will be saved in real time. Don't forget to use 'Undo' and 'Return' appropriately.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0dd475c61ef1cbf24789c8de19ec02dd.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After the Great Clash, the world was destroyed, broken and divided into several realms. Each realm was managed by Gods, but the Gods abandoned humans.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/42a4f199c3d28d87542b43d4aa62e1b6.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a 'Contender', you have a mission to advance to the throne of God. When a Contender reaches the throne of a God, they are crowned as a new God.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/98994b1b14cae235fb200191c7fc42fc.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various traps and footholds await you on your way to the throne of God. Break through these safely and advance towards the top.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/ad7552b392cdf7fa5a6dec574d55382a.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you throw a sphere with your right hand, after a while it will move to where it was. This is the Contender's unique power 'Blink'.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/3fd28d680b8988f68b68abc786a423c0.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Destroy medals hidden throughout the realm to level up. Leveling up has several benefits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.poster.avif?t=1689338499\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.webm?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1911400/extras/0f2742da404cac36d03450a71dd04159.mp4?t=1689338499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your challenge progress will be saved in real time. Don't forget to use 'Undo' and 'Return' appropriately.",
